    %% Egress flows (rbac mode)
    RBACProxy -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>SA Token + SAR"| K8sAPI

    %% Optional
    AuthProxy -.->|"TCP/6379<br/>Optional TLS<br/>Password"| Redis

